label: Create Update Tombstone Event
definition: Create Update Tombstone Event, based on W3C PROV Data Model (https://www.w3.org/TR/prov-o/)

label: Id
definition: The unique identifier of the Create Update Tombstone Event, this includes the version of the object

label: Type
definition: The DOI to the FDO type of the object

label: Activity
definition: Based on the prov-ontology Activity Class, https://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity

label: Was Associated With
definition: Contains zero a reference to one or more prov:Agent objects that were associated with the Activity

label: Ended At Time
definition: The date and time when the activity ended, in ISO 8601 format, http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#endedAtTime

label: Used
definition: The unique identifier of the prov:Entity that was used in the Activity (as indicated at @id in the Activity Class), http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#used

label: Comment
definition: A comment about the activity, https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment
examples: ['This activity was created by the user']

label: Change Value
definition: The json patch object that describes the changes made to the object as opposed to the previous version, empty if this is a ods:Create or ods:Tombstone activity

label: Entity
definition: Based on the prov-ontology Entity Class, https://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity

label: Value
definition: The full object that is the result of the prov:Activity, the structure of this object is defined by the `@type` field. When the `prov:Activity` is of type `ods:Tombstone`, this field is empty
examples: [{'@id': 'https://hdl.handle.net/20.5000.1025/ABC-DEF-GHI', '@type': 'ods:Mapping', 'ods:ID': 'https://hdl.handle.net/20.5000.1025/ABC-DEF-GHI', 'ods:type': 'https://doi.org/10.15468/1a2b3c', 'schema:version': 1, 'schema:name': 'Default Mapping for Herbarium of University of Coimbra (COI)', 'schema:description': 'The default mapping for the Herbarium of the University of Coimbra (COI) to the Darwin Core standard.', 'schema:dateCreated': '2021-06-01T12:00:00Z', 'ods:creator': 'e2befba6-9324-4bb4-9f41-d7dfae4a44b0', 'ods:Mapping': {'ods:DefaultMapping': [{'ods:physicalSpecimenIdType': 'cetaf'}, {'ods:type': 'ZoologyVertebrateSpecimen'}, {'ods:organisationId': 'https://ror.org/05xg72x27'}], 'ods:FieldMapping': [{'ods:physicalSpecimenId': 'dwc:catalogNumber'}]}, 'ods:mappingDataStandard': 'dwc'}]

label: Was Revision Of
definition: The unique identifier (handle) of the previous version of the object, only present when prov:Activity is of type ods:Update and ods:Tombstone

label: Was Generated By
definition: The unique identifier of the prov:Activity that generated the Entity (as indicated at @id in the Activity Class), http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasGeneratedBy

label: Has Prov Agent
definition: Contains zero or more prov:Agent objects

label: Agent
definition: Description of the agents connected to the digital object

label: Name
definition: Full name of the agent

label: Role Name
definition: Indicates the role of the agent, https://schema.org/roleName

label: Start Date
definition: Date the agent began the role

label: End Date
definition: Date the agent ended the role

label: Role Order
definition: Order of the agent in the role. Can be used to indicate the order of importance

label: Email
definition: Email of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Url
definition: URL of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Has Identifier
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Identifier objects
